Package: skysense-conf
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
         ${shlibs:Depends},
         sed,
         uuid-runtime,
         gpw,
Description: Any common files for skysense, e.g. skysense.conf.
  Contains any common files for skysense, mainly skysense.conf
  which is shared between other skysense packages.

